title: The Siete Interview: Compton Upbringing, County Jail Squabbles, Meeting his Mom at 18 & More
description:
Siete sits down with T-Rell and AD to reminisce on how they know each other, growing up in Compton, DJ Mustard, Sauce Walka and more!
https://www.instagram.com/siete7x__/
https://www.instagram.com/_kingtrell/ 
https://www.instagram.com/iitsad/
--
2:25 - Getting put on by ADs little brother, getting the name Siete
12:00 - Not getting a DJ Mustard beat yet, not being thirsty for it 
17:17 - Seeing his mom for the first time, them both crying, how he found her 
24:23 - County jail squabbles, homies showing him structure, putting him onto game 
32:43 - Learning how to get his music up on the DSPs, monetizing videos and music, wanting to learn the music biz on his own
39:36 - Not knowing what to think seeing AD on No Jumper podcasting and acting in “DAVE”
